window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Despite his betrayal of Jesus, Judas wants a second chance. When a new prophet is found, he sees the opportunity for redemption. A marketing guru, Judas has never understood why God didn't use his powers to market Jesus to the masses, gaining more followers and saving the world. Intent on showing off his marketing prowess, Judas convinces God to let him return to earth. The new prophet is a woman who possesses supernatural abilities and must overcome horrifying dreams about a serial killer in order to share her ministry. But things don't go according to plan as Judas turns the life of the new prophet into a marketing circus. A supernatural thriller, <i>The Judas Gospel</i> takes listeners on a terrifying journey as Judas comes to realize that in mixing commerce with God, bigger isn't always better. </p>"; 
